{"tid":1485913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致香港人，多謝你地未放棄","createTime":"2019-08-18T17:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T17:17:46.000Z","uid":305912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ed0b8c6c393eb1cbc27aec8565c72e49a69241da","tid":1485913,"uid":305912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:12:00.000Z","msg":"見到出面好多post都討論緊金鐘走唔走既事，但係我好想開一個講講今日。<br />\n<br />\n由六月到依家發生左好多事，好多令人唔開心既事。本來都擔心818人數會唔會特別少，但係見到今日仲有170萬+既人肯願意出黎真係覺得好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論係和理非定係勇武派都好，好多謝你地未放棄，多謝你地守護我地既屋企。真係辛苦哂你地，如果攰既話沖個涼用熱水浸下腳，好好訓一覺。<br />\n<br />\n希望呢個post可以鼓勵到或者俾到你一個好心情<br />\n亦可以係留言留低你想講既野<br />\n給螢幕前既你、香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"9dd1492b3e4647538aec8f81d22652249582b9f0","tid":1485913,"uid":305912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:13:09.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"311f3fa4100e277d4d481b4fc7230f6c14dc1c04","tid":1485913,"uid":305912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:14:57.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4cfc2ff46373be9fcd19f2186adaaa1c749969","tid":1485913,"uid":305912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:15:07.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ff2c56d80f2df80fe8c4bd2516c7f13d1e9c4b","tid":1485913,"uid":305912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:16:40.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"2e5674e70a5b42096326de1a83e74448384d7310","tid":1485913,"uid":305912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"19c516ee57632b813d07ef4be607b1ef76b23636","tid":1485913,"uid":305